data.description: This immaculate recent finish Gallery custom home has everything you could ever ask for! This one of a kind home sits on a half acre that backs up to a pasture for all of the country feel you could ask for while also being centrally located. This home includes 5 bedrooms 4 full bathrooms 3 of them being ensuite bathrooms and 2 half baths, one down stairs one upstairs. The kitchen boast quartz countertops throughout, gas cooktop, double oven, reverse osmosis filtration system for drinking water. Downstairs features master bedroom and bathroom a 2nd bedroom with an ensuite bathroom. The downstairs area also has a half bath as well as a utility room that features a sink. Upstairs the home has a media room that is plumbed for a wet bar as well as 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The bedroom to the right of the stair case has a 2nd master bathroom ensuite that is almost identical to the primary master downstairs.  3D tour is attached or available upon request
